data.description: *****OFFERS DUE BY SATURDAY, JAN 20TH @ 8PM*****Welcome to your new family haven at 1434 W 41St. Street. This delightful 4 bed, 3 bath home offers a perfect blend of history charm and modern comfort. Just a few blocks from ODU and the vibrant Ghent neighborhood, you will enjoy an open concept living space and kitchen, spacious bedrooms, cathedral ceilings, porcelain tile, REAL HARDWOOD FLOORS, TWO massive balconies a BUILT GENERATOR and much more! Are you a practicing professional such as a Professor, Doctor, Lawyer, Doctor, CPA, etc? Ask about special financing at 0 down with no mortgage insurance! VA ASSUMABLE AT 2.5%.
